<h1>AsiaInspection Mobile App: Now Manage Your Supply Chain on the Go!</h1>

<p><b>Hong Kong, September 27, 2013</b> - AsiaInspection, a leading provider of <a href="/quality-control-services">quality control services</a> helping brands, retailers and importers secure their global supply chain today announces the launch of its <a href="/mobile">mobile application</a> which will allow <a href="/quality-control-services/product-and-manufacturing-inspections">inspections</a>, <a href="/quality-control-services/supplier-audit-programs
">audits</a> and <a href="/quality-control-services/laboratory-testing">lab tests</a> to be conveniently ordered from mobile devices.</p>
	
	<div style="float:right;">
		<img src="https://s3.asiainspection.com/images/app_PR.jpg" alt="AsiaInspection Mobile App – Supply Chain Management Platform" />
	</div>

<p>"International buyers are by their very essence mobile. Empowering them to access supplier KPI's, book inspections, tests and supplier audits and approve reports on the go, will increase their efficiency and control over their import operations." said Sebastien Breteau, CEO, AsiaInspection.</p>

<p>The <a href="/mobile">AI App</a> offers new and improved features including:</p>
<ul>
	<li>Detailed <a href="/quality-control-services/product-and-manufacturing-inspections">inspection</a>, <a href="/quality-control-services/supplier-audit-programs">audit</a> and <a href="/quality-control-services/laboratory-testing">lab tests</a> reports delivered online</li>
	<li>An <a href="/register">online dashboard</a> to monitor and benchmark your supply chain Key Performance Indicators (KPI’s) and rank suppliers</li>
	<li>Approve or reject shipments</li>
	<li>Seamlessly place orders and manage scheduling</li>
</ul>

<p>The <a href="/mobile">AI App</a> is free and can be downloaded for <a target="_blank" href="https://itunes.apple.com/us/app/id589783645">iOS</a>, <a target="_blank" href="https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.asiainspection">Android</a> or accessed on the web at <a target="_blank" href="/mobile">www.asiainspection.com/mobile</a>.</p>

<p>Product inspections are $<span style='font-size:inherit;' class='priceIA'></span> USD in China, India, Bangladesh, Vietnam, Thailand, Africa and Latin America; $<span style='font-size:inherit;' class='priceIE'></span> USD in Europe and anywhere else in Asia. Factory, social and environmental audits are $<span style='font-size:inherit;' class='priceAT'></span> USD.</p>

